#*****************************************************************

INSTALL:

Install as a tomcat Filter in the application web.xml  and provide the 
"configurationFile" pointing to the configuration file (the path is relative 
to the installed directory). 

For example:

    	<!-- HPSS Filter -->
	<filter>
		<filter-name>StagerFilter</filter-name>
		<filter-class>esgf.node.stager.web.StagerFilter</filter-class>
		<init-param>		
			<param-name>configurationFile</param-name>
			<param-value>/WEB-INF/stager.properties</param-value>
		</init-param>
	</filter>
	<filter-mapping>
		<filter-name>StagerFilter</filter-name>
		<url-pattern>/*</url-pattern>
	</filter-mapping>